### 🟡 MEDIUM — Missing Negative/Edge-Case Tests

| Missing scenario | Risk |
|---|---|
| `GetProduct` with non-existent SKU → should return `null` | Null-reference bugs in callers |
| `UpdatePrice` with non-existent SKU → should throw `KeyNotFoundException` | Unhandled exceptions in prod |
| `ApplyBulkDiscount(1.0m)` → prices become 0 | Business logic error undetected |
| `ImportFromCsv` with malformed input | `IndexOutOfRangeException` / `FormatException` crash in prod |
| `RemoveProduct` then `GetProduct` → should return `null` | Deletion not actually working |

**Fix pattern:**
```csharp
[TestMethod]
[ExpectedException(typeof(KeyNotFoundException))]
public void UpdatePrice_NonExistentSku_Throws()
{
    _catalog.UpdatePrice("MISSING", 5.00m);
}
```

